title: Fool Coverage with Manny MUA and Laura Lee Trailer
description:
Welcome to Fool Coverage a weekly podcast with the 2 infamous besties Manny MUA and Laura Lee! Two OG social media influencers who love all things beauty, fashion, pop culture but with a little bit of drama! Each week they discuss what’s happening in their lives, the digital space, and all things pop culture… who wants the real tea?! 
From friendship to being canceled to brand owners who’ve experienced it all, nothing is off-limits ! 
Tune in every week for a new episode!
